		cs_bytes int,
		s_timetaken int

	AS
	BEGIN

		@result = EXTRACT
			s_date DateTime,
			s_time string,
			s_sitename string,
			cs_method string,
			cs_uristem string,

			VALUES(1,2),(2,4)
